@database Render_Toaster.guide

@node Main "Render:  Toaster"

   The Toaster render module is used to transfer images directly from ImageFX
   to one of the Video Toaster framebuffers.

   @{u}Bank:@{uu}  Framestore Bank to transfer to (DV1 or DV2).

   @{u}Program Output:@{uu}  Determines what kind of Switcher action to
      take after transferring the image.  "None" does nothing, "Take"
      performs a take switch, and "Auto" performs the current transition
      effect.

   @{u}Transfer:@{uu}  Transfer image to the Video Toaster.

   @{u}TAKE:@{uu}  Direct the Switcher to do a Take transition.

   @{u}AUTO:@{uu}  Direct the Switcher to do an Auto transition.

@endnode

